title: CSE 5431 - Systems II: Introduction to Operating Systems
description: Introduction to operating system concepts: process, CPU scheduling, memory management, file system and storage, and multi-threaded programming.Prereq: 5042 or equiv. Not open to students with credit for 2431 or 660.
professors: Feng Qin,Yinqian Zhang,Gojko Babic,Doreen Close,Adam Champion,George Green
